    TimeBarMarker

    public class TimeBarNowMarker
extends TimeBarMarkerImpl
    An extension of the TimeBarMarkerImpl that will always mark the current time.

    ATTENTION: not a clean solution by now - demonstration only. Users of this class have to take care of the thread.
